[+]---------------------------------------[+]
 | ][ Automatic Security Level Upgrader ][ |
[+]---------------------------------------[+]
 |                                         |
 | Ever wanted to automatically promote    |
 | users as they reach a certain level on  |
 | your BBS? This MPL will do just that!   |
 |                                         |
 | If a new user (level 10) calls your     |
 | BBS more than 20 times or posts 20 or   |
 | more messages, they will upon next      |
 | call be upgraded to the next level.     |
 |                                         |
 | If they're a regular (level 20) and     |
 | make 50 calls and have posted 50 times  |
 | then they get upgraded again to the     |
 | next level.                             |
 |                                         |
 | The levels are customisable as are the  |
 | steps between levels and the number of  |
 | calls and posts required to reach the   |
 | next level.                             |
 |                                         |
 |                                         |
